{"tid":1546073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一句講曬 淆底既人 拍卡再跳閘 跳左既入黎打個卡","createTime":"2019-09-06T06:45:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T09:53:41.000Z","uid":12952,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2f430a6a7dc34358290346ef9c6af7f59916fdb6","tid":1546073,"uid":12952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:45:12.000Z","msg":"知你淆底喇<br />\n唔緊要 俾個方法你<br />\n錢照畀閘照跳<br />\n又無話過閘一定要推旋轉棍<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">舊閘要拍完卡照跳<br />\n新閘就拍左閘跳右閘</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n為左保護真正跳閘既人<br />\n全世界都要做到全民跳閘<br />\n咁啲查飛狗根本分唔到<br />\n最低成本 破壞黨鐵機制<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">舊旋轉閘<br />\n拍卡照跳<br />\n新閘<br />\n其實我左拗 左手拍卡跳右閘</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n總之做到全民跳閘<br />\n等同blackblock難以分辨<br />\n<br />\n跳左4日<br />\n根本無人理我<br />\n你今日跳左未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全民跳閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b015b2e9e299c2d9e8c434b1afbc798196e860a","tid":1546073,"uid":12952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:45:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dfda868f9a2b5de98dd9d598e5d21257d65eec4f","tid":1546073,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:45:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b73056adf217debd1ca1ce52efd26b66dbaaca8c","tid":1546073,"uid":12952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:45:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"43ced1716c805e07eaabb1dcea363bc4850358ac","tid":1546073,"uid":12952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:45:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"59ba832491134b69d9603c25f5cab8197a67fee4","tid":1546073,"uid":264097,"like"